descriptionHtml:
This file will no longer be supported. I have left this file up for those of you who prefer this darker non-vendor version.The updated version has been renamed to Hrothgar Sanctuary and can be found here. [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11749]Hrothgar Sanctuary[/url]
_______________________________
My apologies but, those of you who wish to upgrade to the new version will need to remove all items from any containers in the original version and deselect it before installing  [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11749]Hrothgar Sanctuary[/url]
All future expansions will be made to this new version.
_______________________________
Another file of mine that you may like:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8677]Landscaped_Player_Homes_WIP[/url]
